{
  "stem": "945.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we took it for granted, and we didn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we didn't seek any shelter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But anyway, the Romanians gave up the territories.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they were no match for the Soviet giant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so in about two days or a day and a half, the Romanians evacuated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Russians, the Soviet Union, came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the communists, it was a big day of celebration.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For most of the other Jewish people in town, it was a very uncertain time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know what the new regime, so to speak, or what the new government, was going to be.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What are they going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in an indirect way, the Jewish people felt that it can't be any worse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It might be better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] However, that also proved to be wrong.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The new government came in-- introduced their--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russian government introduced their style of governing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they had their own designs for the area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They weren't there to liberate anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were there to pursue their goals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now that we know how the Soviet Union acted, and how they progressed with their ideology, they first-- they first tried to declare who was their enemy.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they eliminated their enemy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In their philosophy and in their way of thinking, any merchant, any little storekeeper, any little free enterprise, or any person that made a living out for themself, for them, it was a-- a counterrevolutionary.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a capitalist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It didn't fit their ideology.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So first thing we find out is on a given day, their forces came in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their police forces came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
